sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Host  as Application Node
    participant App   as Spring Boot Container
    participant Vault as HashiCorp Vault
    participant DB    as MySQL Database

    Host->>App: docker run (VAULT_TOKEN injected via ENV)
    Note over App: Bootstrap Phase — Spring Cloud Vault
    App->>Vault: GET /v1/secret/data/monetique-eye (Token Auth)
    Vault->>Vault: Validate token and check access policies

    alt Authorised
        Vault-->>App: DB_USERNAME, DB_PASSWORD, JWT_SECRET, GROQ_API_KEY
        Note over App: Inject into ApplicationContext — no disk files touched
        App->>DB: Initialize Datasource connection
        DB-->>App: Handshake OK
        Note over App: HTTP port open — ready to serve
    else Unauthorised
        Vault-->>App: 403 Forbidden
        Note over App: Bootstrap failure — container exits
    end
